{"data":[{"id":562170697,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bcd8f7d6a54829b444dba8cdfc6fc4c2","url_token":"deng-bing-er-58","name":"邓冰er","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bcd8f7d6a54829b444dba8cdfc6fc4c2","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562170697","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546060272,"updated_time":1546060272,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e一位层主的评论中复制的：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本文作者timeline：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-在知乎收藏：“导数压轴小题5秒一个”“你不得不看的高考数学无耻得分法”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-在知乎提问：“河北大学有没有数学系？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-在知乎发表文章“本人证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，将于2019年1月1日在知乎上公开发表”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-发表知乎提问“如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-在上述问题的所有回答下面，包括各种有理有据的分析、策略提供、建议发arxiv或给期刊投稿、给大学数学系写信，这些所有回答下面复读机：“1月1日知乎公开发表论文，欢迎观看。”而不理会这些信息是否会对自己有帮助。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-表示自己的论文“漏洞没有，但没有发表论文的平台。”“但我真的证明出来了，想发表论文，不知道该怎么发”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是真的不明白“1月1日零点发”这个行为除了引人关注还有什么合理的理由。想发表就直接发出来，让大家看看到底对不对，想保护著作权就去发arxiv或期刊，大家不是没给你提供门路。搞一个“1月1日发”，无非是在这段时间之前，让你的文章保持一个在“证出来”和“没证出来”的叠加态，吸一波关注，而不是一上来就被啪啪打脸。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以为自己想出了哥猜“很简单，只是没人发现”的证法，以为数学界都没你聪明全没想到，这真的没什么，只是年少的狂妄而已，坦然地给大家看了，哪怕是收获一堆嘲笑，自己能在这个过程中有所收获就好，搞一个“一月一日零点发”，装神弄鬼，哗众取宠是干什么呢？没有天赋不丢人，考不上好大学也不丢人，好好努力就行了。但是你还年轻，未来还有无限的可能，思维能力也还没到达人生的巅峰，不要在这个时候就自甘堕落，成为一个沽名钓誉之徒。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"一位层主的评论中复制的：本文作者timeline：-在知乎收藏：“导数压轴小题5秒一个”“你不得不看的高考数学无耻得分法”-在知乎提问：“河北大学有没有数学系？”-在知乎发表文章“本人证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，将于2019年1月1日在知乎上公开发表”-发表知乎…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1202\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment